{"tid":103572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"80隻獵鷹坐專機打獵","createTime":"2017-02-01T12:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T12:18:52.000Z","uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6466d7ec14b8f85370d06a2995cac4d6283b26ab","tid":103572,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:12:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>【星島日報報道】</strong>卡塔爾航空公司一架客機出現奇景，機艙內有八十隻獵鷹，佔滿多行座位。不過，牠們的翼都被綁着。原來是一名沙特王子把這批獵鷹運送作打獵之用。機長一名朋友把奇景拍下，放上社交網站reddit分享，引起網民熱議。根據卡塔爾航空公司的規定，每隻獵鷹運費介乎九十至五百英鎊（八百七十多至四千八百多港元），視乎目的地而定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/3zHKo.UPIVmMVLjDyjhR7g--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztjaD02NjI7Y3I9MTtjdz03MDQ7ZHg9MDtkeT0wO2ZpPXVsY3JvcDtoPTQ3MjtpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc1O3c9NTAy/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2017-01-31/8a2ccfb0-e802-11e6-94f8-a1081a697133_EAGLE_2017013116151368764_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3zHKo.UPIVmMVLjDyjhR7g--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztjaD02NjI7Y3I9MTtjdz03MDQ7ZHg9MDtkeT0wO2ZpPXVsY3JvcDtoPTQ3MjtpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc1O3c9NTAy%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2017-01-31%2F8a2ccfb0-e802-11e6-94f8-a1081a697133_EAGLE_2017013116151368764_detail.jpg&h=5facac67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/80%E7%8D%B5%E9%B7%B9%E5%9D%90%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F%E5%8E%BB%E6%89%93%E7%8D%B5-221120526.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F80%25E7%258D%25B5%25E9%25B7%25B9%25E5%259D%2590%25E9%25A3%259B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%258D%25B5-221120526.html&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=756a29ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/80%E7%8D%B5%E9%B7%B9%E5%9D%90%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F%E5%8E%BB%E6%89%93%E7%8D%B5-221120526.html</a>"},{"pid":"e5546de40e1d5cfedff9307c00ad7896e800becb","tid":103572,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:18:52.000Z","msg":"程機皇室開支用左幾多